@node bugs "Ooo.. an undocumented feature.."


                            @{b}- V1.0 BUGS FIXED -@{ub}


- Memory buffer overrun bug fixed in list caching routine.  Engine
  enhanced and optimized for further speed gain.

- Same bug also found in string search routine (wow!) - Engine also
  enhanced.

- Strange bug mentioned by only one user in the upload routine using "ul"
  in conjunction with Unpack Diz flag - still not experienced by myself or
  anyone else but investigating!

@endnode
